21static inline isc_result_t
22fromtext_sig(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
23 isc_token_t token;
24 unsigned char c;
25 long i;
26 dns_rdatatype_t covered;
27 char *e;
28 isc_result_t result;
29 dns_name_t name;
30 isc_buffer_t buffer;
31 uint32_t time_signed, time_expire;
32
33 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_sig);
34
35 UNUSED(type);
36 UNUSED(rdclass);
37 UNUSED(callbacks);
38
39 /*
40 * Type covered.
41 */
42 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
43 false));
44 result = dns_rdatatype_fromtext(&covered, &token.value.as_textregion);
45 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS && result != ISC_R_NOTIMPLEMENTED) {
46 i = strtol(DNS_AS_STR(token), &e, 10);
47 if (i < 0 || i > 65535)
48 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
49 if (*e != 0)
50 RETTOK(result);
51 covered = (dns_rdatatype_t)i;
52 }
53 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(covered, target));
54
55 /*
56 * Algorithm.
57 */
58 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
59 false));
60 RETTOK(dns_secalg_fromtext(&c, &token.value.as_textregion));
61 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, &c, 1));
62
63 /*
64 * Labels.
65 */
66 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
67 false));
68 if (token.value.as_ulong > 0xffU)
69 RETTOK(ISC_R_RANGE);
70 c = (unsigned char)token.value.as_ulong;
71 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, &c, 1));
72
73 /*
74 * Original ttl.
75 */
76 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
77 false));
78 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
79
80 /*
81 * Signature expiration.
82 */
83 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
84 false));
85 RETTOK(dns_time32_fromtext(DNS_AS_STR(token), &time_expire));
86 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(time_expire, target));
87
88 /*
89 * Time signed.
90 */
91 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
92 false));
93 RETTOK(dns_time32_fromtext(DNS_AS_STR(token), &time_signed));
94 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(time_signed, target));
95
96 /*
97 * Key footprint.
98 */
99 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_number,
100 false));
101 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(token.value.as_ulong, target));
102
103 /*
104 * Signer.
105 */
106 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
107 false));
108 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
109 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
110 if (origin == NULL)
111 origin = dns_rootname;
112 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin, options, target));
113
114 /*
115 * Sig.
116 */
117 return (isc_base64_tobuffer(lexer, target, -2));
118}

120static inline isc_result_t
121totext_sig(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
122 isc_region_t sr;
123 char buf[sizeof("4294967295")];
124 dns_rdatatype_t covered;
125 unsigned long ttl;
126 unsigned long when;
127 unsigned long exp;
128 unsigned long foot;
129 dns_name_t name;
130 dns_name_t prefix;
131 bool sub;
132
133 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_sig);
134 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
135
136 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
137
138 /*
139 * Type covered.
140 */
141 covered = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
142 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
143 /*
144 * XXXAG We should have something like dns_rdatatype_isknown()
145 * that does the right thing with type 0.
146 */
147 if (dns_rdatatype_isknown(covered) && covered != 0) {
148 RETERR(dns_rdatatype_totext(covered, target));
149 } else {
150 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", covered);
151 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
152 }
153 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
154
155 /*
156 * Algorithm.
157 */
158 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", sr.base[0]);
159 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
160 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
161 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
162
163 /*
164 * Labels.
165 */
166 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%u", sr.base[0]);
167 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
168 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
169 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
170
171 /*
172 * Ttl.
173 */
174 ttl = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
175 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
176 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%lu", ttl);
177 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
178 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
179
180 /*
181 * Sig exp.
182 */
183 exp = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
184 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
185 RETERR(dns_time32_totext(exp, target));
186
187 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
188 RETERR(str_totext(" (", target));
189 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
190
191 /*
192 * Time signed.
193 */
194 when = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
195 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
196 RETERR(dns_time32_totext(when, target));
197 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
198
199 /*
200 * Footprint.
201 */
202 foot = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
203 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
204 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%lu", foot);
205 RETERR(str_totext(buf, target));
206 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
207
208 /*
209 * Signer.
210 */
211 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
212 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
213 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &sr);
214 isc_region_consume(&sr, name_length(&name));
215 sub = name_prefix(&name, tctx->origin, &prefix);
216 RETERR(dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
217
218 /*
219 * Sig.
220 */
221 RETERR(str_totext(tctx->linebreak, target));
222 if (tctx->width == 0) /* No splitting */
223 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&sr, 60, "", target));
224 else
225 RETERR(isc_base64_totext(&sr, tctx->width - 2,
226 tctx->linebreak, target));
227 if ((tctx->flags & DNS_STYLEFLAG_MULTILINE) != 0)
228 RETERR(str_totext(" )", target));
229
230 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
231}

233static inline isc_result_t
234fromwire_sig(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
235 isc_region_t sr;
236 dns_name_t name;
237
238 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_sig);
239
240 UNUSED(type);
241 UNUSED(rdclass);
242
243 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
244
245 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
246 /*
247 * type covered: 2
248 * algorithm: 1
249 * labels: 1
250 * original ttl: 4
251 * signature expiration: 4
252 * time signed: 4
253 * key footprint: 2
254 */
255 if (sr.length < 18)
256 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
257
258 isc_buffer_forward(source, 18);
259 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, 18));
260
261 /*
262 * Signer.
263 */
264 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
265 RETERR(dns_name_fromwire(&name, source, dctx, options, target));
266
267 /*
268 * Sig.
269 */
270 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sr);
271 isc_buffer_forward(source, sr.length);
272 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
273}
274
275static inline isc_result_t
276towire_sig(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
277 isc_region_t sr;
278 dns_name_t name;
279 dns_offsets_t offsets;
280
281 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_sig);
282 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
283
284 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
285 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
286 /*
287 * type covered: 2
288 * algorithm: 1
289 * labels: 1
290 * original ttl: 4
291 * signature expiration: 4
292 * time signed: 4
293 * key footprint: 2
294 */
295 RETERR(mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, 18));
296 isc_region_consume(&sr, 18);
297
298 /*
299 * Signer.
300 */
301 dns_name_init(&name, offsets);
302 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &sr);
303 isc_region_consume(&sr, name_length(&name));
304 RETERR(dns_name_towire(&name, cctx, target));
305
306 /*
307 * Signature.
308 */
309 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sr.base, sr.length));
310}

312static inline int
313compare_sig(ARGS_COMPARE) {
314 isc_region_t r1;
315 isc_region_t r2;
316 dns_name_t name1;
317 dns_name_t name2;
318 int order;
319
320 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
321 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
322 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_sig);
323 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
324 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
325
326 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
327 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
328
329 INSIST(r1.length > 18);
330 INSIST(r2.length > 18);
331 r1.length = 18;
332 r2.length = 18;
333 order = isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2);
334 if (order != 0)
335 return (order);
336
337 dns_name_init(&name1, NULL);
338 dns_name_init(&name2, NULL);
339 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
340 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
341 isc_region_consume(&r1, 18);
342 isc_region_consume(&r2, 18);
343 dns_name_fromregion(&name1, &r1);
344 dns_name_fromregion(&name2, &r2);
345 order = dns_name_rdatacompare(&name1, &name2);
346 if (order != 0)
347 return (order);
348
349 isc_region_consume(&r1, name_length(&name1));
350 isc_region_consume(&r2, name_length(&name2));
351
352 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
353}

355static inline isc_result_t
356fromstruct_sig(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
357 dns_rdata_sig_t *sig = source;
358
359 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_sig);
360 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
361 REQUIRE(sig->common.rdtype == type);
362 REQUIRE(sig->common.rdclass == rdclass);
363 REQUIRE(sig->signature != NULL || sig->siglen == 0);
364
365 UNUSED(type);
366 UNUSED(rdclass);
367
368 /*
369 * Type covered.
370 */
371 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(sig->covered, target));
372
373 /*
374 * Algorithm.
375 */
376 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(sig->algorithm, target));
377
378 /*
379 * Labels.
380 */
381 RETERR(uint8_tobuffer(sig->labels, target));
382
383 /*
384 * Original TTL.
385 */
386 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(sig->originalttl, target));
387
388 /*
389 * Expire time.
390 */
391 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(sig->timeexpire, target));
392
393 /*
394 * Time signed.
395 */
396 RETERR(uint32_tobuffer(sig->timesigned, target));
397
398 /*
399 * Key ID.
400 */
401 RETERR(uint16_tobuffer(sig->keyid, target));
402
403 /*
404 * Signer name.
405 */
406 RETERR(name_tobuffer(&sig->signer, target));
407
408 /*
409 * Signature.
410 */
411 return (mem_tobuffer(target, sig->signature, sig->siglen));
412}

414static inline isc_result_t
415tostruct_sig(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
416 isc_region_t sr;
417 dns_rdata_sig_t *sig = target;
418 dns_name_t signer;
419
420 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_sig);
421 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
422 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
423
424 sig->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
425 sig->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
426 ISC_LINK_INIT(&sig->common, link);
427
428 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sr);
429
430 /*
431 * Type covered.
432 */
433 sig->covered = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
434 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
435
436 /*
437 * Algorithm.
438 */
439 sig->algorithm = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
440 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
441
442 /*
443 * Labels.
444 */
445 sig->labels = uint8_fromregion(&sr);
446 isc_region_consume(&sr, 1);
447
448 /*
449 * Original TTL.
450 */
451 sig->originalttl = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
452 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
453
454 /*
455 * Expire time.
456 */
457 sig->timeexpire = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
458 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
459
460 /*
461 * Time signed.
462 */
463 sig->timesigned = uint32_fromregion(&sr);
464 isc_region_consume(&sr, 4);
465
466 /*
467 * Key ID.
468 */
469 sig->keyid = uint16_fromregion(&sr);
470 isc_region_consume(&sr, 2);
471
472 dns_name_init(&signer, NULL);
473 dns_name_fromregion(&signer, &sr);
474 dns_name_init(&sig->signer, NULL);
475 RETERR(name_duporclone(&signer, mctx, &sig->signer));
476 isc_region_consume(&sr, name_length(&sig->signer));
477
478 /*
479 * Signature.
480 */
481 sig->siglen = sr.length;
482 sig->signature = mem_maybedup(mctx, sr.base, sig->siglen);
483 if (sig->signature == NULL)
484 goto cleanup;
485
486
487 sig->mctx = mctx;
488 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
489
490 cleanup:
491 if (mctx != NULL)
492 dns_name_free(&sig->signer, mctx);
493 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
494}
495
496static inline void
497freestruct_sig(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
498 dns_rdata_sig_t *sig = (dns_rdata_sig_t *) source;
499
500 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
501 REQUIRE(sig->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_sig);
502
503 if (sig->mctx == NULL)
504 return;
505
506 dns_name_free(&sig->signer, sig->mctx);
507 if (sig->signature != NULL)
508 isc_mem_free(sig->mctx, sig->signature);
509 sig->mctx = NULL;
510}

535static inline dns_rdatatype_t
536covers_sig(dns_rdata_t *rdata) {
537 dns_rdatatype_t type;
538 isc_region_t r;
539
540 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_sig);
541
542 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
543 type = uint16_fromregion(&r);
544
545 return (type);
546}
